## <a name="introduction"></a><span data-ttu-id="23319-105">介绍</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23319-105">Introduction</span></span>  
 <span data-ttu-id="23319-106">使用<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Localize>控件保留在网页上显示本地化后的文本的位置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23319-106">Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Localize> control to reserve a location on a Web page in which to display localized text.</span></span>  
  
