>  <span data-ttu-id="23319-107">外部的控件`body`元素将被忽略。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23319-107">Controls that are outside the `body` element are ignored.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="23319-108"><xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Localize>控件继承自<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>控件并等同于它在各方面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23319-108">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Localize> control inherits from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control and is identical to it in every way.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23319-109"><xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Localize>控件用于在设计时将可本地化的静态文本与其他静态文本区分开来。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23319-109">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Localize> control is used at design time to distinguish static text that can be localized from other static text.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23319-110">尽管<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label>让您可以将样式应用到显示的文本，<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Localize>控件却没有。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23319-110">Although the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label> control allows you to apply a style to the displayed text, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Localize> control does not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23319-111">你可以以编程方式管理通过设置控件中显示的文本<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>属性，继承自<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>控件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23319-111">You can programmatically manage the text displayed in the control by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property, inherited from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control.</span></span>  
  
> [!CAUTION]
>  <span data-ttu-id="23319-112">此控件用于显示用户输入，这可能包括恶意客户端脚本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23319-112">This control can be used to display user input, which might include malicious client script.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23319-113">检查从客户端的可执行脚本、 SQL 语句或其他代码之前发送应用程序中显示的任何信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23319-113">Check any information that is sent from a client for executable script, SQL statements, or other code before displaying it in your application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23319-114">ASP.NET 提供了用户输入到脚本块和 HTML 的输入的请求验证功能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23319-114">ASP.NET provides an input request validation feature to block script and HTML in user input.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23319-115">验证服务器控件还提供用于评估用户输入。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23319-115">Validation server controls are also provided to assess user input.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23319-116">有关详细信息，请参阅[保护标准控件](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/f3e7718f-63d0-44a3-bd5f-48cc2059c2a8)，[如何： 保护对脚本攻击在 Web 应用程序通过应用 HTML 编码为字符串](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/6f67973f-dda0-45a1-ba9d-e88532d7dc5b)，和[中验证用户输入ASP.NET Web Pages](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/4ad3dacb-89e0-4cee-89ac-40a3f2a85461)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23319-116">For more information, see [Securing Standard Controls](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/f3e7718f-63d0-44a3-bd5f-48cc2059c2a8), [How to: Protect Against Script Exploits in a Web Application by Applying HTML Encoding to Strings](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/6f67973f-dda0-45a1-ba9d-e88532d7dc5b), and [Validating User Input in ASP.NET Web Pages](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/4ad3dacb-89e0-4cee-89ac-40a3f2a85461).</span></span>  
  
